       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE PSI11106         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDCONTR4 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSHCDNT03  END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDEC00   END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDHEADER END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA      END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY PSCV1110.
       COPY PSCV1111.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY VIAL0030.
       COPY VIAW0030.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY PSCK0001.
       COPY PSCK0002.
       COPY PSCK0003.
       COPY VIAW0050.
       COPY BRCL1020.
      *
      *CONVERSAO DE DATAS
       COPY AQCW0005.
      *TRATAMENTO RCODES
       COPY AQCL0001.
       COPY AQCW0009.
      *TRATAMENTO CONTAS
       COPY AQCW0008.
      * Linkage para Rotina de Valida��o de Conta
       COPY SXCL0002.
       COPY SXCL0170.
       COPY SXCL0045.
       COPY SXCL0405.
       COPY SXCW0902.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-PSCONTRA               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSCONTRA'.
           05 CON-PSHCONTR               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSHCONTR'.
           05 CON-PSPRECAR               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSPRECAR'.
           05 CON-PSHEADER               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSHEADER'.
           05 CON-PRG-NAM                PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI11106'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME                PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI11106'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-FIC-AGUARDA-EXEC        PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-FIC-CREDITO             PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-FIC-CRED-EFECT          PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-FIC-EM-PROC             PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-FIC-CRED-NEFEC          PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE PSI11106         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '0000-MAINLINE.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV1110-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV1110-ASE               TO PSCV1111-ASE.
      *
           PERFORM 1200-OBTEM-CONTRATO
              THRU 1299-OBTEM-CONTRATO-EXIT.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   1200-OBTEM-CONTRATO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1200-OBTEM-CONTRATO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1200-OBTEM-CONTRATO'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV1110-COCCLI            TO PSCONTRAT-COCCLI.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COTSERV           TO PSCONTRAT-COTSERV.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT   COCCLI
                     , CODESC
                     , CONCLIA
                     , CONATRA
                     , CONSEQA
                     , CONCLIB
                     , CONATRB
                     , CONSEQB
                     , CONCLIC
                     , CONATRC
                     , CONSEQC
                     , COCLICCC
                     , CONATCCC
                     , COSEQCCC
                     , CODABR
                     , COSITU
                     , COPREC
                     , COTMOV
                     , CONTRY
                     , COILCO
                     , CONOTOS
                     , CONOTBS
                     , COOGER
                     , COEMAIL
                     , CONOTOE
                     , CONOTBE
                     , COAGEN
                     , COASSA
                     , COASSB
                     , COASSC
                     , COCACE
                     , COCCONF
                     , COPASS
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEEST
                     , COCONTAA
                     , COCONTAB
                     , COCONTAC
                     , COCONTACCC
                     , IDESCRDEF
                 INTO
                       :PSCONTRAT-COCCLI
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CODESC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATRA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATRB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATRC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCLICCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATCCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COSEQCCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CODABR
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COSITU
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COPREC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COTMOV
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONTRY
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COILCO
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTOS
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTBS
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COOGER
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COEMAIL
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTOE
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTBE
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COAGEN
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COASSA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COASSB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COASSC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCACE
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCCONF
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COPASS
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CUSERID
                     , :PSCONTRAT-HTIMEEST
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTACCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-IDESCRDEF
                 FROM PSCONTRAT4
                 WHERE
                    COCCLI = :PSCONTRAT-COCCLI
                 AND COTSERV = :PSCONTRAT-COTSERV
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-PSCONTRA
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
                 ELSE
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCCLI
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CODESC
                      TO PSCV1111-CODESC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONCLIA
                      TO PSCV1111-CONCLIA
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCONTAA
                      TO PSCV1111-COCONTAA
      *             MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONSEQA
      *               TO PSCV1111-CONSEQA
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONCLIB
                      TO PSCV1111-CONCLIB
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCONTAB
                      TO PSCV1111-COCONTAB
      *             MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONSEQB
      *               TO PSCV1111-CONSEQB
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONCLIC
                      TO PSCV1111-CONCLIC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCONTAC
                      TO PSCV1111-COCONTAC
      *             MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONSEQC
      *               TO PSCV1111-CONSEQC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCLICCC
                      TO PSCV1111-COCLICCC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCONTACCC
                      TO PSCV1111-COCONTACCC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-IDESCRDEF
                      TO PSCV1111-IDESCRDEF
      *             MOVE PSCONTRAT-COSEQCCC
      *               TO PSCV1111-COSEQCCC
      *
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CODABR   TO AQCW0005-DT98
                    PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
                       THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT
                    MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10    TO PSCV1111-CODABR
      *
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COSITU
                      TO PSCV1111-COSITU
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COPREC
                      TO PSCV1111-COPREC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COTMOV
                      TO PSCV1111-COTMOV
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONTRY
                      TO PSCV1111-CONTRY
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COILCO
                      TO PSCV1111-COILCO
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONOTOS
                      TO PSCV1111-CONOTOS
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONOTBS
                      TO PSCV1111-CONOTBS
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COOGER
                      TO PSCV1111-COOGER
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COEMAIL
                      TO PSCV1111-COEMAIL
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONOTOE
                      TO PSCV1111-CONOTOE
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-CONOTBE
                      TO PSCV1111-CONOTBE
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COAGEN
                      TO PSCV1111-COAGEN
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COASSA
                      TO PSCV1111-COASSA
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COASSB
                      TO PSCV1111-COASSB
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COASSC
                      TO PSCV1111-COASSC
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCACE
                      TO PSCV1111-COCACE
                    MOVE PSCONTRAT-COCCONF
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCONF
                    IF NOT VIAL0001-VISUALIZACAO
                        IF PSCONTRAT-COSITU = PSCK0002-SITCT-INACTIVO
                           MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                             TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                           MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                             TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
                           MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COSITU
                             TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
                        END-IF
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.
       1299-OBTEM-CONTRATO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV1110-ADE               TO PSCV1111-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2150-GUARDA-HISTORICO
                 THRU 2159-GUARDA-HISTORICO-EXIT
           END-IF

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-MODIFICA-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-MODIFICA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF
           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *Val Cliente
           IF PSCV1110-COCCLI IS NUMERIC
            AND PSCV1110-COCCLI NOT EQUAL ZEROS
                PERFORM 2160-VALIDA-NCLI
                   THRU 2169-VALIDA-NCLI-EXIT
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCCLI
                TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
           END-IF.
      * CONTA A
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2110-VALIDA-CONTA-A
                 THRU 2119-VALIDA-CONTA-A-EXIT
           END-IF.
      * CONTA B
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND PSCV1110-CONCLIB NOT EQUAL ZEROES
              PERFORM 2120-VALIDA-CONTA-B
                 THRU 2129-VALIDA-CONTA-B-EXIT
           END-IF.
      * CONTA C
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND PSCV1110-CONCLIC NOT EQUAL ZEROES
              PERFORM 2130-VALIDA-CONTA-C
                 THRU 2139-VALIDA-CONTA-C-EXIT
           END-IF.
      * VALIDA CODIGO DE PRECARIO
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND PSCV1110-COPREC NOT EQUAL SPACES
              PERFORM 2180-VALIDA-PREC
                 THRU 2189-VALIDA-PREC-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
      * VALIDA TIPO DE MOVIMENTACAO
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS  AND
              PSCV1110-COTMOV NOT EQUAL PSCONTRAT-COTMOV
              PERFORM 2150-VALIDA-TMOV
                 THRU 2159-VALIDA-TMOV-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND PSCV1110-COCLICCC NOT EQUAL ZEROES
              PERFORM 2190-VALIDA-CCC
                 THRU 2199-VALIDA-CCC-EXIT
           END-IF.
      * Valida email Ordenante
           IF PSCV1110-CONOTOE EQUAL PSCK0002-NOTE-S  AND
              PSCV1110-COEMAIL EQUAL SPACES

              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV1111-COEMAIL-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-NOT-MAIL       TO PSCV1111-COEMAIL-MSG
           END-IF.
      *
       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2110-VALIDA-CONTA-A
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2110-VALIDA-CONTA-A.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-VALIDA-CONTA-A.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV1110-COCONTAA  '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  PSCV1110-COCONTAA     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

            IF PSCV1110-CONCLIA IS NOT NUMERIC
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                  TO PSCV1111-CONCLIA-S
                MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CONCLIA
                  TO PSCV1111-CONCLIA-MSG
            END-IF.
            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               IF PSCV1110-COCONTAA IS NOT NUMERIC
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                     TO PSCV1111-COCONTAA-S
                   MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCONTAA
                     TO PSCV1111-COCONTAA-MSG
               END-IF
            END-IF.
      *     IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *        IF PSCV1110-CONSEQA IS NOT NUMERIC
      *            MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
      *              TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *            MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *              TO PSCV1111-CONSEQA-S
      *            MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CONSEQA
      *              TO PSCV1111-CONSEQA-MSG
      *        END-IF
      *     END-IF.
            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONCLIA  TO  AQCW0008-NCLI23
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONATRA  TO  AQCW0008-NATR23
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONSEQA  TO  AQCW0008-NSEQ23
               MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTAA TO  AQCW0008-CONTA23

               PERFORM 2140-VALIDA-CONTA
                  THRU 2149-VALIDA-CONTA-EXIT

               MOVE SXCL0170-RCODE TO AQCW0009-RCODE
               PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
                  THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT
      *
               IF AQCL0001-COM-ERROS
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO PSCV1111-COCONTAA-S
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCONTAA
                    TO PSCV1111-COCONTAA-MSG
               END-IF
            END-IF.
       2119-VALIDA-CONTA-A-EXIT.
            EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2120-VALIDA-CONTA-B
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2120-VALIDA-CONTA-B.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2120-VALIDA-CONTA-B.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
            IF PSCV1110-CONCLIB IS NOT NUMERIC
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                  TO PSCV1111-CONCLIB-S
                MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CONCLIB
                  TO PSCV1111-CONCLIB-MSG
            END-IF.
            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               IF PSCV1110-COCONTAB IS NOT NUMERIC
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                     TO PSCV1111-COCONTAB-S
                   MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCONTAB
                     TO PSCV1111-COCONTAB-MSG
               END-IF
            END-IF.
      *     IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *        IF PSCV1110-CONSEQB IS NOT NUMERIC
      *            MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
      *              TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *            MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *              TO PSCV1111-CONSEQB-S
      *            MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CONSEQB
      *              TO PSCV1111-CONSEQB-MSG
      *        END-IF
      *     END-IF.
            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONCLIB  TO  AQCW0008-NCLI23
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONATRB  TO  AQCW0008-NATR23
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONSEQB  TO  AQCW0008-NSEQ23
               MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTAB TO  AQCW0008-CONTA23

               PERFORM 2140-VALIDA-CONTA
                  THRU 2149-VALIDA-CONTA-EXIT

               MOVE SXCL0170-RCODE TO AQCW0009-RCODE
               PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
                  THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT
               IF AQCL0001-COM-ERROS
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO PSCV1111-COCONTAB-S
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCONTAB
                    TO PSCV1111-COCONTAB-MSG
               END-IF
            END-IF.
       2129-VALIDA-CONTA-B-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2130-VALIDA-CONTA-C
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2130-VALIDA-CONTA-C.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2130-VALIDA-CONTA-C.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
            IF PSCV1110-CONCLIC IS NOT NUMERIC
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                  TO PSCV1111-CONCLIC-S
                MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CONCLIC
                  TO PSCV1111-CONCLIC-MSG
            END-IF.
            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               IF PSCV1110-COCONTAC IS NOT NUMERIC
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                     TO PSCV1111-COCONTAC-S
                   MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCONTAC
                     TO PSCV1111-COCONTAC-MSG
               END-IF
            END-IF.
      *     IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *        IF PSCV1110-CONSEQC IS NOT NUMERIC
      *            MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
      *              TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *            MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *              TO PSCV1111-CONSEQC-S
      *            MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CONSEQC
      *              TO PSCV1111-CONSEQC-MSG
      *        END-IF
      *     END-IF.
            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONCLIC  TO  AQCW0008-NCLI23
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONATRC  TO  AQCW0008-NATR23
      *        MOVE PSCV1110-CONSEQC  TO  AQCW0008-NSEQ23
               MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTAC TO  AQCW0008-CONTA23

               PERFORM 2140-VALIDA-CONTA
                  THRU 2149-VALIDA-CONTA-EXIT

               MOVE SXCL0170-RCODE TO AQCW0009-RCODE
               PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
                  THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT
               IF AQCL0001-COM-ERROS
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO PSCV1111-COCONTAC-S
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCONTAC
                    TO PSCV1111-COCONTAC-MSG
               END-IF
            END-IF.
       2139-VALIDA-CONTA-C-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2140-VALIDA-CONTA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2140-VALIDA-CONTA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2140-VALIDA-CONTA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
            CALL 'ARREBENTA'

            INITIALIZE SXCL0170-DATA.
      *
            MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS      TO SXCL0170-VERSAO.
      *     SET SXCL0170-V300             TO TRUE.
            MOVE CON-PRG-NAM              TO SXCL0170-PGMC  .
            MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-CS017       TO SXCL0170-TTR.
            MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID        TO SXCL0170-JOBNC .
            MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN     TO SXCL0170-USERC .
            MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ            TO SXCL0170-PGMQC .
            MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK        TO SXCL0170-RCODE .
            MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-EXE        TO SXCL0170-ESTR  .
            MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL        TO SXCL0170-APTR  .
            MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG       TO SXCL0170-HCLI.
            MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL       TO SXCL0170-VNCR.
            MOVE PSCK0002-PNOME-N         TO SXCL0170-PNOME.
            MOVE AQCW0008-CONTA23         TO SXCL0170-CONTA.
            MOVE PSCV1110-COCCLI          TO SXCL0170-NCLI.

            CALL SXCL0170-ROTINA USING    SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                          SXCL0170-DATA.
       2149-VALIDA-CONTA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2150-VALIDA-TMOV
      *  se existem ficheiros em processamento nao e possivel
      *  alterar o tipo de mocimentacao
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-VALIDA-TMOV.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-VALIDA-TMOV.'     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV1110-COCCLI            TO PSHEADER-HRNCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-FIC-AGUARDA-EXEC  TO WS-FIC-AGUARDA-EXEC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-FIC-CREDITO       TO WS-FIC-CREDITO     .
           MOVE PSCK0002-FIC-CRED-EFECT    TO WS-FIC-CRED-EFECT  .
           MOVE PSCK0002-FIC-EM-PROC       TO WS-FIC-EM-PROC     .
           MOVE PSCK0002-FIC-CRED-NEFEC    TO WS-FIC-CRED-NEFEC  .

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT   HRDINT
                     , HRNFIC
                 INTO  :PSHEADER-HRDINT
                     , :PSHEADER-HRNFIC
                 FROM PSHEADER
                 WHERE  HRNCLI  =  :PSHEADER-HRNCLI
                   AND  HRSITU IN (:WS-FIC-AGUARDA-EXEC
                                  ,:WS-FIC-CREDITO
                                  ,:WS-FIC-CRED-EFECT
                                  ,:WS-FIC-EM-PROC
                                  ,:WS-FIC-CRED-NEFEC  )
              FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-PSHEADER               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
                 WHEN DB2-OK
                 WHEN DB2-DUPREC
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO PSCV1111-COTMOV-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-TMOV-FIC-PR
                                           TO PSCV1111-COTMOV-MSG
                 WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                    CONTINUE
                 WHEN OTHER
                    SET VIAL0002-ABEND-DB2 TO TRUE
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.
       2159-VALIDA-TMOV-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2160-VALIDA-NCLI
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2160-VALIDA-NCLI.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2160-VALIDA-NCLI.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *  SE O CLIENTE NAO EXISTIR NA BANKA, NAO E VALIDO
           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS      TO SXCL0045-VERSAO.
      *    SET SXCL0045-V300             TO TRUE.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ            TO SXCL0045-DPGMQ.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN     TO SXCL0045-DUSERC.
           MOVE SPACES                   TO SXCL0045-DTACE.
      *---
           MOVE 'S'                      TO SXCL0045-DVNCR .
           MOVE '3'                      TO SXCL0045-WTVCLI.
           MOVE 'S'                      TO SXCL0045-WBLOQ .
           MOVE 'N'                      TO SXCL0045-WPNOME.
      *---
           MOVE ZERO                     TO SXCL0045-DRCODE.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCCLI          TO SXCL0045-CRNCLI.
      *
           CALL SXCL0045-ROTINA USING SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                      SXCL0045-DATA.
      *
           IF SXCL0045-DRCODE GREATER PSCK0002-RCODE-INF
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
           END-IF.
       2169-VALIDA-NCLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2180-VALIDA-PREC
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2180-VALIDA-PREC.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2180-VALIDA-PREC.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV1110-COPREC
             TO PSCDEC00-PRPREC
           MOVE PSCV1110-COTSERV
             TO PSCDEC00-PRTSERV
           MOVE VIAL0001-ORIGEM
             TO PSCDEC00-PRCANAL

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT PRSITU
               INTO  :PSCDEC00-PRSITU
               FROM PSPRECARI
              WHERE PRPREC  = :PSCDEC00-PRPREC
                AND PRCANAL = :PSCDEC00-PRCANAL
                AND PRTSERV = :PSCDEC00-PRTSERV
           END-EXEC.


           MOVE CON-PSPRECAR
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF PSCDEC00-PRSITU = PSCK0002-SITPR-INACTIVO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1111-COPREC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-PRPREC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1111-COPREC-MSG
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO PSCV1111-COPREC-S
                 MOVE PSCK0001-PRPREC-N-EXISTS
                   TO PSCV1111-COPREC-MSG
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       2189-VALIDA-PREC-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2190-VALIDA-CCC
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2190-VALIDA-CCC.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2190-VALIDA-CCC   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           INITIALIZE SXCL0405-DATA.
           INITIALIZE SXCL0002-COMMAREA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS      TO SXCL0405-VERSAO.
      *    SET  SXCL0405-V300                    TO TRUE           .
           MOVE CON-PRG-NAM              TO SXCL0405-DPGMC .
           SET  SXCL0405-CONSULTA-DADOS-CCC      TO TRUE           .
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID        TO SXCL0405-DJOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN     TO SXCL0405-DUSERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ            TO SXCL0405-DPGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK        TO SXCL0405-DRCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-EXE        TO SXCL0405-DESTR .
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL        TO SXCL0405-DAPTR .
           MOVE ZEROES                   TO SXCL0405-DHCLI .
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL       TO SXCL0405-DVNCR .
           MOVE PSCK0002-PNOME-N         TO SXCL0405-WPNOME.
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-COCLICCC        TO SXCL0405-WNCLI .
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-CONATCCC        TO SXCL0405-WNATR .
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-COSEQCCC        TO SXCL0405-WNSEQ .
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTACCC      TO SXCL0405-CONTA .

           PERFORM CALL-SXRM0405
              THRU CALL-SXRM0405-EXIT.
      *
           IF SXCL0405-DRCODE GREATER PSCK0002-RCODE-INF
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-COCLICCC
                TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF SXCL0405-CCNCLD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONCLIA
      *       OR SXCL0405-CCNATD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONATRA
      *       OR SXCL0405-CCNSED NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONSEQA
              OR SXCL0405-CCCONTAD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-COCONTAA
                 IF SXCL0405-CCNCLD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONCLIB
      *          OR SXCL0405-CCNATD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONATRB
      *          OR SXCL0405-CCNSED NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONSEQB
                 OR SXCL0405-CCCONTAD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-COCONTAB
                    IF SXCL0405-CCNCLD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONCLIC
      *             OR SXCL0405-CCNATD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONATRC
      *             OR SXCL0405-CCNSED NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-CONSEQC
                    OR SXCL0405-CCCONTAD NOT EQUAL PSCV1110-COCONTAC
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                         TO PSCV1111-COCONTACCC-S
                       MOVE PSCK0001-ASSOC-CCC-DO-INEX
                         TO PSCV1111-COCONTACCC-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDA-CCC-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2150-MODIFICA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-GUARDA-HISTORICO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-GUARDA-HISTORICO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN'  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

            PERFORM 2160-SEQUENCIA-CONTRATO
               THRU 2160-SEQUENCIA-CONTRATO-EXIT.
      *     PERFORM 2320-MOVE-DADOS
      *        THRU 2329-MOVE-DADOS-EXIT.
            MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN       TO PSHCDNT03-CHDENC
            MOVE PSCK0002-SITCT-INACTIVO   TO PSHCDNT03-CHSITU

           EXEC SQL
                INSERT INTO PSHCONTRA3
                       (  CHCCLI
                        , CHDESC
                        , CHNCLIA
                        , CHNATRA
                        , CHNSEQA
                        , CHNCLIB
                        , CHNATRB
                        , CHNSEQB
                        , CHNCLIC
                        , CHNATRC
                        , CHNSEQC
                        , CHCLICCC
                        , CHNATCCC
                        , CHSEQCCC
                        , CHDABR
                        , CHDENC
                        , CHSITU
                        , CHPREC
                        , CHTMOV
                        , CHNTRY
                        , CHILCO
                        , CHNOTOS
                        , CHNOTBS
                        , CHOGER
                        , CHEMAIL
                        , CHNOTOE
                        , CHNOTBE
                        , CHAGEN
                        , CHASSA
                        , CHASSB
                        , CHASSC
                        , CHCACE
                        , CHCCONF
                        , CHPASS
                        , CUSERID
                        , HTIMEEST
                        , CHTSERV
                        , CHZALT
                        , CHCONTAA
                        , CHCONTAB
                        , CHCONTAC
                        , CHCONTACCC
                        , IDESCRDEF  )
               VALUES (:PSCONTRAT-COCCLI
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CODESC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATRA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATRB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATRC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCLICCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONATCCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COSEQCCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CODABR
                     , :PSHCDNT03-CHDENC
                     , :PSHCDNT03-CHSITU
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COPREC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COTMOV
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONTRY
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COILCO
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTOS
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTBS
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COOGER
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COEMAIL
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTOE
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CONOTBE
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COAGEN
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COASSA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COASSB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COASSC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCACE
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCCONF
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COPASS
                     , :PSCONTRAT-CUSERID
                     , :PSCONTRAT-HTIMEEST
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COTSERV
                     , :PSHCDNT03-CHZALT
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAA
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAB
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-COCONTACCC
                     , :PSCONTRAT-IDESCRDEF  )
           END-EXEC.


           MOVE CON-PSHCONTR               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2159-GUARDA-HISTORICO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       2160-SEQUENCIA-CONTRATO.
      ******************************************************************
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2160-SEQUENCIA-CONTRATO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE  VIAL0030-COMMAREA.

           SET  VIAL0030-SOMA-1            TO TRUE            .
           MOVE PSCK0002-CSEQ-CHZALT       TO VIAL0030-CSEQUEN.

      *
           CALL VIAL0030-NM-ROTINA USING VIAL0030-COMMAREA
BCI202*                                  VIAL0002-COMMAREA.
BCI202                                   ETCL0002-COMMAREA.

BCI202*    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
BCI202     IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAL0030-NSEQUEN-1      TO PSHCDNT03-CHZALT
           ELSE
              SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL      TO TRUE
              MOVE PSCK0003-ERR-VIAR0030   TO SXCW0902-MSGID
              PERFORM SXCP0902-ESCREVE-MSG
                 THRU SXCP0902-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2160-SEQUENCIA-CONTRATO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-MODIFICA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-MODIFICA-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-MODIFICA-DADOS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

            PERFORM 2220-MOVE-DADOS
               THRU 2229-MOVE-DADOS-EXIT.

           EXEC SQL
                 UPDATE
                PSCONTRAT4
                SET    COCCLI     = :PSCONTRAT-COCCLI
                     , CODESC     = :PSCONTRAT-CODESC
                     , CONCLIA    = :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIA
                     , CONATRA    = :PSCONTRAT-CONATRA
                     , CONSEQA    = :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQA
                     , CONCLIB    = :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIB
                     , CONATRB    = :PSCONTRAT-CONATRB
                     , CONSEQB    = :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQB
                     , CONCLIC    = :PSCONTRAT-CONCLIC
                     , CONATRC    = :PSCONTRAT-CONATRC
                     , CONSEQC    = :PSCONTRAT-CONSEQC
                     , COCLICCC   = :PSCONTRAT-COCLICCC
                     , CONATCCC   = :PSCONTRAT-CONATCCC
                     , COSEQCCC   = :PSCONTRAT-COSEQCCC
                     , CODABR     = :PSCONTRAT-CODABR
                     , COSITU     = :PSCONTRAT-COSITU
                     , COPREC     = :PSCONTRAT-COPREC
                     , COTMOV     = :PSCONTRAT-COTMOV
                     , CONTRY     = :PSCONTRAT-CONTRY
                     , COILCO     = :PSCONTRAT-COILCO
                     , CONOTOS    = :PSCONTRAT-CONOTOS
                     , CONOTBS    = :PSCONTRAT-CONOTBS
                     , COOGER     = :PSCONTRAT-COOGER
                     , COEMAIL    = :PSCONTRAT-COEMAIL
                     , CONOTOE    = :PSCONTRAT-CONOTOE
                     , CONOTBE    = :PSCONTRAT-CONOTBE
                     , COAGEN     = :PSCONTRAT-COAGEN
                     , COASSA     = :PSCONTRAT-COASSA
                     , COASSB     = :PSCONTRAT-COASSB
                     , COASSC     = :PSCONTRAT-COASSC
                     , COCACE     = :PSCONTRAT-COCACE
                     , COCCONF    = :PSCONTRAT-COCCONF
                     , COPASS     = :PSCONTRAT-COPASS
                     , COTELF     = :PSCONTRAT-COTELF
                     , CUSERID    = :PSCONTRAT-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEEST   = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
                     , COIIPURG   = :PSCONTRAT-COIIPURG
                     , COIIMREG   = :PSCONTRAT-COIIMREG
                     , COIIEBORDO = :PSCONTRAT-COIIEBORDO
                     , COIIEBORDB = :PSCONTRAT-COIIEBORDB
                     , COTSERV    = :PSCONTRAT-COTSERV
                     , COIIFORMT  = :PSCONTRAT-COIIFORMT
                     , COCONTAA   = :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAA
                     , COCONTAB   = :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAB
                     , COCONTAC   = :PSCONTRAT-COCONTAC
                     , COCONTACCC = :PSCONTRAT-COCONTACCC
                     , IDESCRDEF  = :PSCONTRAT-IDESCRDEF
                 WHERE
                    COCCLI = :PSCONTRAT-COCCLI
                 AND COTSERV = :PSCONTRAT-COTSERV
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-PSCONTRA               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1111-COCCLI-MSG
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2299-MODIFICA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2220-MOVE-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2220-MOVE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2220-MOVE-DADOS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *converting date
           MOVE PSCV1110-CODABR   TO AQCW0005-DTX10.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98     TO PSCONTRAT-CODABR .
      *
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCCLI
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCCLI.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COTSERV
             TO PSCONTRAT-COTSERV
           MOVE PSCV1110-CODESC
             TO PSCONTRAT-CODESC .
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONCLIA
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONCLIA.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTAA
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCONTAA.
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-CONSEQA
      *      TO PSCONTRAT-CONSEQA.
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONCLIB
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONCLIB.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTAB
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCONTAB.
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-CONSEQB
      *      TO PSCONTRAT-CONSEQB.
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONCLIC
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONCLIC.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTAC
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCONTAC.
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-CONSEQC
      *      TO PSCONTRAT-CONSEQC.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCLICCC
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCLICCC.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCONTACCC
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCONTACCC.
           MOVE PSCV1110-IDESCRDEF
             TO PSCONTRAT-IDESCRDEF.
      *    MOVE PSCV1110-COSEQCCC
      *      TO PSCONTRAT-COSEQCCC.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COPREC
             TO PSCONTRAT-COPREC .
           MOVE PSCV1110-COTMOV
             TO PSCONTRAT-COTMOV .
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONTRY
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONTRY .
           MOVE PSCV1110-COILCO
             TO PSCONTRAT-COILCO .
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONOTOS
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONOTOS.
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONOTBS
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONOTBS.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COOGER
             TO PSCONTRAT-COOGER .
           MOVE PSCV1110-COEMAIL
             TO PSCONTRAT-COEMAIL.
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONOTOE
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONOTOE.
           MOVE PSCV1110-CONOTBE
             TO PSCONTRAT-CONOTBE.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COAGEN
             TO PSCONTRAT-COAGEN .
           MOVE PSCV1110-COASSA
             TO PSCONTRAT-COASSA.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COASSB
             TO PSCONTRAT-COASSB.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COASSC
             TO PSCONTRAT-COASSC.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCACE
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCACE.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COCCONF
             TO PSCONTRAT-COCCONF.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COTELF
             TO PSCONTRAT-COTELF.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I
             TO PSCONTRAT-CUSERID.
           MOVE PSCV1110-COIIPURG
             TO PSCONTRAT-COIIPURG
           MOVE PSCV1110-COIIMREG
             TO PSCONTRAT-COIIMREG
           MOVE PSCV1110-COIIEBORDO
             TO PSCONTRAT-COIIEBORDO
           MOVE PSCV1110-COIIEBORDB
             TO PSCONTRAT-COIIEBORDB
           MOVE PSCV1110-COIIFORMT
             TO PSCONTRAT-COIIFORMT
           MOVE PSCV1110-COTSERV
             TO PSCONTRAT-COTSERV.
      *
       2229-MOVE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2320-MOVE-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2320-MOVE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2320-MOVE-DADOS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *converting date
           MOVE PSCV1110-CODABR   TO AQCW0005-DTX10.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98     TO PSHCDNT03-CHDABR .
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN
                                  TO PSHCDNT03-CHDENC .
      *
